%define _optlevel s

Name: stellarium
Version: 0.18.2
Release: alt1

Group: Education
Summary: Astronomical Sky Simulator
Url: http://www.stellarium.org/
License: GPLv2

Source0: %name-%version.tar

BuildPreReq: cmake rpm-macros-cmake

